<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
      xml:lang="en"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      lang="en"
      metal:use-macro="context/main_template/macros/master"
      i18n:domain="plonede.policy">

<body>

  <metal:content-core fill-slot="content-core">


<div class="row margin">
    <div class="col-sm">
        <h2>Demo</h2>
        <p>Auf diesen Seiten können Sie Plone und seine Funktionen testen. Bitte beachten Sie, dass es sich um
            Demo-Seiten handelt. Die Inhalte der Seiten werden in regelmäßigen Abständen zurückgesetzt.</p>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-4">
                <div class="plonede-box">
                    <h3>Plone 5.2</h3>
                    <p><strong>Offizielle Demo mit Python 3 bereitgestellt von der Plone Community</strong></p>
                    <img class="image-inline img-fluid"
                         src="${portal_url}/resolveuid/3e2a18c8bb784c01af3818111579a6aa/@@images/image/preview"
                         data-linktype="image" data-scale="preview" data-val="3e2a18c8bb784c01af3818111579a6aa"/>
                    <p><a href="http://demo.plone.org" rel="noopener" target="_blank">http://demo.plone.org</a></p>
                    <h4>Version</h4>
                    <p>Plone 5.2<br/>Python 3.7</p>
                    <h4>Erweiterungen</h4>
                    <p><a href="https://pypi.org/project/plone.app.multilingual/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">plone.app.multilingual</a>
                    </p>
                    <ul class="languages">
                        <li><img alt="Deutsch" src="${portal_url}/++plone++plonede.policy/flag-de.png"/></li>
                        <li><img alt="English" src="${portal_url}/++plone++plonede.policy/flag-uk.png"/></li>
                        <li><img alt="Spanish" src="${portal_url}/++plone++plonede.policy/flag-es.png"/></li>
                        <li><img alt="Euskara" src="${portal_url}/++plone++plonede.policy/flag-eu.png"/></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-4">
                <div class="plonede-box">
                    <h3>Plone 5.2</h3>
                    <p><strong>Nightly Build mit Python 2 bereitgestellt von der Plone Comunity</strong></p>
                    <img class="image-inline img-fluid"
                         src="${portal_url}/resolveuid/e0751ad5ab17416586a31d0ff021313d/@@images/image/preview"
                         data-linktype="image" data-scale="preview" data-val="e0751ad5ab17416586a31d0ff021313d"/>
                    <p><a href="http://demo-latest-py2.plone.de" rel="noopener" target="_blank">http://demo-latest-py2.plone.de</a>
                    </p>
                    <h4>Version</h4>
                    <p>Plone 5.2<br/>Python 2.7</p>
                    <h4>Erweiterungen</h4>
                    <p><a href="https://pypi.org/project/plone.app.multilingual/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">plone.app.multilingual</a>
                    </p>
                    <ul class="languages">
                        <li><img alt="Deutsch" src="${portal_url}/++plone++plonede.policy/flag-de.png"/></li>
                        <li><img alt="English" src="${portal_url}/++plone++plonede.policy/flag-uk.png"/></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-4">
                <div class="plonede-box">
                    <h3>Plone 5.2</h3>
                    <p><strong>Nightly Build mit Python 3 bereitgestellt von der Plone Comunity</strong></p>
                    <img class="image-inline img-fluid"
                         src="${portal_url}/resolveuid/b05713907a164bbe9a31051760e455bd/@@images/image/preview"
                         data-linktype="image" data-scale="preview" data-val="b05713907a164bbe9a31051760e455bd"/>
                    <p><a href="http://demo-latest-py3.plone.de" rel="noopener" target="_blank">http://demo-latest-py3.plone.de</a>
                    </p>
                    <h4>Version</h4>
                    <p>Plone 5.2<br/>Python 3.6</p>
                    <h4>Erweiterungen</h4>
                    <p><a href="https://pypi.org/project/plone.app.multilingual/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">plone.app.multilingual</a>
                    </p>
                    <ul class="languages">
                        <li><img alt="Deutsch" src="${portal_url}/++plone++plonede.policy/flag-de.png"/></li>
                        <li><img alt="English" src="${portal_url}/++plone++plonede.policy/flag-uk.png"/></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="row margin">
    <div class="col-sm">
        <div class="plonede-box">Project X</div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="row margin">
    <div class="col-sm">
        <div class="plonede-box">Mitmachen</div>
    </div>
</div>

  <div class="row margin">
    <div class="col-sm-12" id="news_heading">
        <h2>News und Events</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-8" id="news">
        <div class="row"
             tal:define="news python: view.news()">
            <div class="col-sm-6">
                <div class="featured-news"
                     tal:define="item python: news[0]">
                    <a href="" tal:attributes="href python: item['url']">
                    <img class="image-inline img-fluid"
                         tal:condition="python: item.get('tag', False)"
                         tal:replace="structure python: item['tag']"
                         />
                    <h2 tal:content="python: item['title']"></h2>
                    <p tal:content="python: item['description']"></p>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 news-items">
                <div class="news-item"
                     tal:repeat="item python: news[1:]">
                    <a href=""
                        tal:attributes="href python: item['url'];
                                        title python: item['description']">
                    <img class="image-left"
                         tal:condition="python: item.get('tag', False)"
                         tal:replace="structure python: item['tag']"
                         />
                    <h2 tal:content="python: item['title']"></h2>
                </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-4" id="events">
        <div class="plonede-box">
            <div tal:repeat="item python: view.events()">
              <a tal:attributes="href python: item['url']">
              <span class="dtstart pat-moment"
                    title="${python:item['start'].isoformat()}"
                    data-pat-moment="format:DD.MM.YYYY"
                    data-date="${python: item['start'].isoformat()}"
                    >
                ${python: item['start'].ctime()}
              </span>
              <h2 tal:content="python: item['title']"></h2>
              <p tal:content="python: item['description']"></p>
              </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

  </metal:content-core>

</body>

</html>
